dct_title_s: Rhodos 1:100,000 : the ultimate travel map solution / Ray Media Enterprises
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depth shown by bathymetric isolines. Map shows roads, paths, ferry routes, international boarders, archaeological sites, tourist sites, ruins, harbors, airports, elevation. "Mondia touristik."
